data.description: Welcome to your dream family home located just 12 miles from Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport. This beautifully designed 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom house offers the perfect blend of space, style, and convenience. Key-Features: Spacious 5 bedrooms: This home boasts five generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for your family and guests. En Suite Primary bedroom: The primary bedroom includes a luxurious ensuite bathroom, ensuring a private retreat. Fully finished basement: A fully finished basement adds extra living space and versatility to this already spacious home. Which includes a full kitchen, spacious media room, 1 bedroom, 1 full bathroom, workout room and more. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful 5-bedroom home your own.
